- content_for :title do
  Our Programs
= nav_at 'Programs'

- content_for :hero do
  %section.hero-slider
    %ul
      %li
        %h1 Intense, collaborative, hands-on.
      %li
        %h1 Our approach to education is holistic...We blend A world-class education with experience, fun, adventure, and collaboration.
      %li
        %h1 We expect a lot in a short period of time. We figure you do too. Our program is intense and unparalleled.
      %li
        %h1 Sure, there are lectures, but nothing can substitute for experience. At Primary Code  you practice what you learn with live clients.
      %li
        %h1 We like to have fun and we want your experience to be fun &mdash; work hard, play hard.
      %li
        %h1 A coding network for life: for help, collaboration, job opportunities, to bounce ideas, for lifelong career friendships. We believe in this.

%ul.tiles
  %li.t-col.w-1-3
    .web-dev-program
      = link_to web_dev_path, class: 't-block hoverable' do
        %span.off-screen Links to Web Development Immersive course description.
        .t-content
          %h2 Web Development Immersive
          .what
            %p An immersive 10-week bootcamp.
          .where
            %h3 Where?
            %p Downtown West Palm Beach, Florida
          .when
            %h3 When?
            %p Next cohort begins September 1, 2016
        .t-more= embedded_svg 'icons/svg/circle-with-plus.svg', class: 'plus'


  %li.t-col.w-1-3
    .part-time-program
      = link_to part_time_path, class: 't-block hoverable' do
        %span.off-screen Links to Part-time Courses course descriptions.
        .t-content
          %h2 Part-time Courses
          .what
            %p An after work part-time program for the working professional.
          .where
            %h3 Where?
            %p Downtown West Palm Beach, Florida
          .when
            %h3 When?
            %p Tracks begin every month.
        .t-more= embedded_svg 'icons/svg/circle-with-plus.svg', class: 'plus'


  %li.t-col.w-1-3
    .summer-program
      = link_to summer_path, class: 't-block hoverable' do
        %span.off-screen Links to Summer of Code course description.
        .t-content
          %h2 Summer of Code
          .what
            %p An immersive summer bootcamp for highschool students.
          .where
            %h3 Where?
            %p Downtown West Palm Beach, Florida
          .when
            %h3 When?
            %p Next cohort begins July 1, 2016
        .t-more= embedded_svg 'icons/svg/circle-with-plus.svg', class: 'plus-dark'


  %li.t-col.w-1-3
    .backend-program
      = link_to backend_path, class: 't-block hoverable' do
        %span.off-screen Links to Summer of Code course description.
        .t-content
          %h2 Backend Immersive
          .what
            %p Take a deep dive into functional programming, the future of the Web with Elixir and Phoenix.
          .where
            %h3 Where?
            %p Downtown West Palm Beach, Florida
          .when
            %h3 When?
            %p Courses begin every month from 6-9 PM on Wednesdays and 9-5 on weekends.
        .t-more= embedded_svg 'icons/svg/circle-with-plus.svg', class: 'plus'


  %li.t-col.w-1-3
    .network
      .t-block
        .t-content
          %p The network you create is as important as the skills you learn. Through team based learning and collaboration you will gain life long friends and coding colleagues.

  %li.t-col.w-1-3
    .launch-program
      = link_to launch_path, class: 't-block hoverable' do
        %span.off-screen Links to Launch Program description.
        .t-content
          %h2 Launch Program
          %p
            %strong Do you need a website?
            Our students, led by instructors, can build your website at minimal to no cost to you.
        .t-more= embedded_svg 'icons/svg/circle-with-plus.svg', class: 'plus'


%section.program-blurb
  %h1 Learning at Primary Code is intense, fun, challenging, and rewarding. It will be a life changing experience!

%ul.tiles
  %li.t-col.w-1-2
    .t-block.mission
      .t-content
        %h2 We are dedicated to your success and to improving the world through technology.
      .t-bottom
        %h3 This is our mission, and an important one. Each and every member of Primary Code takes this charge seriously.

  %li.t-col.w-1-2
    .t-block.network
      .t-content
        %h2 It is important for students to belong to a network in which to flourish from once they graduate.
      .t-bottom
        %h3 Our curriculum is designed to foster teamwork and collaboration.

  %li.t-col.w-1-2
    .t-block.location
      .t-content
        %h2 We are located in the heart of West Palm Beach, within blocks from all major attractions and amenities.
      .t-bottom
        %h3 This provides our students with a rich environment for building lifelong friendships and collaboration networks. And most importantly... to have fun!

  %li.t-col.w-1-2
    .t-block.founder
      .t-content
        %h2 Give us a call, come by and visit.
      .t-bottom
        %h3 We look forward to meeting you.
